channel.title: Need major help!
channel.description: Whenever I try to log into my server it says that I am already logged in and that it wants me to try again. I do that and it says the same thing. I decided to look into the character file to see if the problem was there. Two files popped up "Twilight (which is me)" and "_." I've never seen "_" before so I opened it up to look at it and it had the exact same information as "Twilight" (except for player rights.) So I deleted it and tried to log in again. This time it took a little longer but ended up saying error connecting to server. I tried once more and it said I was logged in still. I went back to characters and "_" popped up again, even tho I didn't try to log in with that. What's the problem!? Please help!
